---
// Components
// - Layout
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
// - UI
import SidebarContent from '../components/blocks/basic/StickySidebar.astro'
import Hero from '../components/blocks/hero/PageHeader.astro'

// Content
// - SEO
const SEO = {
    title: 'LearnFacebookAdsInsights | Privacy Policy',
    description:
        "LearnFacebookAdsInsights privacy policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our website and product."
}
// - Page Header
const header = {
    title: 'Privacy Policy',
    text: 'We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This policy explains how we handle your information.'
}
---

<Layout title={SEO.title} description={SEO.description}>
    <Hero title={header.title} text={header.text} />
    <SidebarContent>
        <div slot="sidebar">
            <h3>Quick Info</h3>
            <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 23 October 2025</p>
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://lfbai.learndata.xyz">lfbai.learndata.xyz</a></p>
            <p><strong>Business Name:</strong> LearnFacebookAdsInsights</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:admin@learndata.xyz">admin@learndata.xyz</a></p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> Nigeria</p>
        </div>
        <div class="basic-text">
            <h4>Introduction</h4>
            <p>
                Welcome to <strong>LearnFacebookAdsInsights</strong> ("we," "our," "us"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our website <a href="https://lfbai.learndata.xyz">lfbai.learndata.xyz</a> ("Website") and our product <strong>LearnFacebookAds Insights</strong>, a Google Sheets™ extension that allows users to automatically pull Facebook Ads data and perform AI-based analysis.
            </p>

            <h4>1. Who We Are</h4>
            <p>
                <strong>Business Name:</strong> LearnFacebookAdsInsights<br>
                <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://lfbai.learndata.xyz">https://lfbai.learndata.xyz</a><br>
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:admin@learndata.xyz">admin@learndata.xyz</a><br>
                <strong>Address:</strong> Nigeria
            </p>
            <p>
                We are the data controller responsible for processing your personal data in accordance with this Privacy Policy and applicable data protection laws, including the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
            </p>

            <h4>2. Data We Collect</h4>
            <p>We collect and process the following categories of personal data:</p>
            
            <h5>a. Information You Provide Directly</h5>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Name, email address, and password when you register or use our extension.</li>
                <li><strong>Billing and payment data:</strong> When you purchase a subscription or service.</li>
                <li><strong>Support information:</strong> When you contact us for assistance or feedback.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5>b. Data Collected Automatically</h5>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Information about how you interact with our Website and extension, such as your IP address, browser type, device information, pages visited, and time spent.</li>
                <li><strong>Cookies and tracking technologies:</strong> Used to improve user experience, analytics, and security.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5>c. Third-Party Data</h5>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Facebook Ads Data:</strong> When you connect your Facebook account via our extension, we access your authorized Facebook Ads data (e.g., campaign performance metrics) strictly for the purpose of generating reports and AI insights within Google Sheets™. We do <strong>not</strong> store or share your Facebook login credentials.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </SidebarContent>
    <SidebarContent classes="bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900">
        <div slot="sidebar">
            <h3>Data Usage</h3>
            <p>
                Understanding how we use your data and the legal basis for processing helps ensure transparency and compliance with data protection laws.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="basic-text">
            <h4>3. How We Use Your Data</h4>
            <p>We process your personal data to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services and extension.</li>
                <li>Authenticate users and provide secure access.</li>
                <li>Process payments and manage subscriptions.</li>
                <li>Offer customer support and respond to inquiries.</li>
                <li>Analyze usage trends to enhance our products.</li>
                <li>Comply with legal obligations and prevent fraud.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We only use your data for legitimate business purposes or with your explicit consent.</p>

            <h4>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h4>
            <p>Under GDPR, we rely on the following lawful bases:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Contract performance:</strong> To provide the service you requested.</li>
                <li><strong>Legitimate interests:</strong> To improve our service and ensure security.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal obligations:</strong> To comply with applicable laws.</li>
                <li><strong>Consent:</strong> When you explicitly agree to specific data uses (e.g., marketing communications).</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>5. Data Retention</h4>
            <p>
                We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or to comply with legal requirements. When data is no longer needed, it will be securely deleted or anonymized.
            </p>
        </div>
    </SidebarContent>
    <SidebarContent>
        <div slot="sidebar">
            <h3>Data Sharing</h3>
            <p>
                Learn about how we share your data with third parties and the safeguards we have in place to protect your information.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="basic-text">
            <h4>6. How We Share Your Data</h4>
            <p>We may share your data with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Service providers and partners</strong> who assist with hosting, analytics, payment processing, or support.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> when required by law or to protect our rights.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We never sell or rent your personal data.</p>
            <p>
                All third-party processors are bound by confidentiality and data protection agreements to ensure your data is handled securely and in compliance with GDPR.
            </p>

            <h4>7. International Data Transfers</h4>
            <p>
                As we operate from Nigeria, your data may be transferred and processed outside the European Economic Area (EEA). We ensure appropriate safeguards (such as Standard Contractual Clauses) are in place to protect your personal data.
            </p>

            <h4>8. Your Rights Under GDPR</h4>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access your personal data.</li>
                <li>Rectify inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
                <li>Request erasure ("right to be forgotten").</li>
                <li>Restrict or object to processing.</li>
                <li>Data portability (receive your data in a usable format).</li>
                <li>Withdraw consent at any time (without affecting prior processing).</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@learndata.xyz">admin@learndata.xyz</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </SidebarContent>
    <SidebarContent classes="bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900">
        <div slot="sidebar">
            <h3>Security & More</h3>
            <p>
                Important information about cookies, data security, and our commitment to protecting your privacy.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="basic-text">
            <h4>9. Cookies and Tracking</h4>
            <p>We use cookies to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Remember user preferences.</li>
                <li>Improve site performance and analytics.</li>
                <li>Support essential site functionality.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                You can control cookies through your browser settings or cookie consent preferences on our Website.
            </p>

            <h4>10. Data Security</h4>
            <p>
                We implement industry-standard technical and organizational measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no online system can guarantee 100% security.
            </p>

            <h4>11. Children's Privacy</h4>
            <p>
                Our services are not directed toward individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us for removal.
            </p>

            <h4>12. Updates to This Policy</h4>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
            </p>
        </div>
    </SidebarContent>
    <SidebarContent>
        <div slot="sidebar">
            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>
            <p>
                Have questions about how we handle your data? We're here to help and ensure your privacy concerns are addressed.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="basic-text">
            <h4>13. Contact Us</h4>
            <p>
                If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>LearnFacebookAdsInsights</strong><br>
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:admin@learndata.xyz">admin@learndata.xyz</a><br>
                <strong>Address:</strong> Nigeria<br>
                <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://lfbai.learndata.xyz">https://lfbai.learndata.xyz</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                <strong>© 2025 LearnFacebookAdsInsights. All rights reserved.</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </SidebarContent>
</Layout>